reviewText: Wonderful job, Jim knows his material and does an excellent job telling us about it.  I've previously known the design perspective only, and now after watching the video, have a good understanding of the operational side of septic systems.  Well worth the $2 watch, and certainly worth owning the video. The back drop for this instructional video was very appropriate.
This is a very well produced item. I found it very informative. It arrived sooner than expected in great condition.
